{
  "texts": [
    "Supplementary Fig. 13 shows a histogram of the sizes of all molecules that are found in the ANI-1xnr dataset, which includes one molecule up to 145 atoms.",
    "The majority are small molecules of similar size or slightly larger than those from which the systems were initialized.",
    "There are many occurrences of molecules in the range of 10-90 atoms.",
    "The largest structures, ascertained by visual inspection, are graphene sheets.",
    "Furthermore, the 1,212 unique PubChem molecules only represent the simulation frames that were selected by the uncertainty estimate."
  ]
}